## Web Project 4 - Veni Vici!

Submitted by: Gamuchirai Constantine MUBAYIWA

About this web app: **A StumbleUpon-like discovery web application that allows users to randomly cycle through various dog breeds, explore their unique traits, and custom-filter their discoveries using an interactive attribute ban list.**

Time spent: **[8]** hours spent in total

